    },
    {
        id: 'history',
        title: 'History',
        description: 'Journey through 5,000 years of tea culture, from ancient Chinese legends to the Boston Tea Party and modern innovations. Explore how tea shaped empires, influenced trade routes, and became the world\'s second most-consumed beverage after water.',
        href: `/${topicSlug}/history/`,
    },
    {
        id: 'technical',
        title: 'Technical Deep Dive',
        description: 'Master the science of brewing with precise temperature, timing, and tea-to-water ratios for every tea type. Learn the chemistry behind extraction, the physics of water quality, and the mathematical principles that underpin consistent, delicious results.',
