    },
    {
        id: 'challenges',
        title: 'Challenges',
        description: 'Common pitfalls in tea preparation and purchasing, with expert solutions for enthusiasts at all levels. Address issues like over-steeping, water quality problems, storage mistakes, and navigating the overwhelming variety of available teas.',
